snippet: Victoria Nuland, a senior State Department official, effectively told them that President Viktor F. Yanukovich must remain in power despite demands for his ouster.
abstract: Senior State Department official Victoria Nuland urges all sides in the Ukrainian crisis to work together to find a solution through peaceful and lawful means.

byline.original: By DAVID M. HERSZENHORN and STEVEN ERLANGER
byline.contributor: David M. Herszenhorn reported from Kiev, and Steven Erlanger from London.

lead_paragraph: Victoria Nuland, a senior State Department official, effectively told them that President Viktor F. Yanukovich must remain in power despite demands for his ouster.

headline.main: American Official Tells Ukraine’s Protest Leaders to Find Peaceful End to Crisis
headline.print_headline: American Official Tells Ukraine’s Protest Leaders to Find Peaceful End to Crisis
